,"tid":1923410,"uid":146588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"你咪破囉, 拎返D口罩都冇意粉佬用架啦= ="},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"跟本歐美國家係因為唔夠口罩<br />\n先叫無病既人唔好戴<br />\n留比醫護同確診既人<br />\n<br />\n中國一爆發就全世界搶口罩<br />\nmade in china既又扣留住唔比出口<br />\n搞到好多係中國設廠既外國公司都拎唔到自己做既口罩<br />\n<br />\n而家中國賣番少少口罩比意大利又當做善事咁"},{"pid":"30e0644f988ba9014b5a12e04975ba9dd48cf611","tid":1923410,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}